{"tid":1205518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果比警察查身份證，可以叫佢出示委任證，打去警署查詢","createTime":"2019-06-11T19:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:48:26.000Z","uid":214897,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c4dd120d7a173119edb3730388d87395962b88","tid":1205518,"uid":214897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:46:21.000Z","msg":"如果比警察查身份證，可以叫佢出示委任證，打去警署查詢，因為委任證都有假。確認左就叫佢過煮。如果有幾萬人叫佢出示<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html#q5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F13_faqs%2Ffaq_g.html%23q5&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvkZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=ddbf7d6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html#q5</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.如何辨認警務人員之身份/警察委任證之真偽？<br />\n<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n當警務人員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。&nbsp;如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署&nbsp;查詢。"},{"pid":"dd70171f912306a0b99fa19a691732d891426c40","tid":1205518,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:47:51.000Z","msg":"4. 如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員應出示委任證，除非:<br />\n(a) 情況不容許;或<br />\n(b) 出示委任證會影響警隊行動及/或危及有關人員的安全;或<br />\n(c) 要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo020.pdf&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvkZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=db86214a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得一試，但最好拖慢黎睇，同問多幾條問題。太多人同時做有機會會俾人破法。"},{"pid":"78d07d8869517ea37d6d956087877928566698d7","tid":1205518,"uid":9193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:02:53.000Z","msg":"排隊問佢地攞委任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7132a001972c7aafa70ebc5328642bc199c480","tid":1205518,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:09:50.000Z","msg":"有冇人整資料庫？<br />\n最好記低d資料放出黎記低哂全部警察的資料"},{"pid":"74e62a0b62cf7bf1dd53f2e1743f623ee32b0f8c","tid":1205518,"uid":255062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:22:38.000Z","msg":"be careful brothers"},{"pid":"60482b6487ae820371009db92d570876060aa4a6","tid":1205518,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:20:12.000Z","msg":"之前比龜逗都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862105b60e35b81473c1904dcaf58fa42b934654","tid":1205518,"uid":214897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd70171f912306a0b99fa19a691732d891426c40","tid":1205518,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:47:51.000Z","msg":"4. 如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員應出示委任證，除非:<br />\n(a) 情況不容許;或<br />\n(b) 出示委任證會影響警隊行動及/或危及有關人員的安全;或<br />\n(c) 要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo020.pdf&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvkZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=db86214a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得一試，但最好拖慢黎睇，同問多幾條問題。太多人同時做有機會會俾人破法。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"如果佢查得人，搜得身。咁應該係情況容許wor。唯一唔容許應該係追緊賊掛。我擔心搜我果個唔係警察，核實完先比佢搜都好合理丫"},{"pid":"662f19323f60231851f628e7bcd07d1516be179d","tid":1205518,"uid":93563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:19:58.000Z","msg":"得閒路過見到狗，可唔可以叫佢羅呢？"},{"pid":"6246dcb03963ea126b29bd9f730531ad05dabb31","tid":1205518,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662f19323f60231851f628e7bcd07d1516be179d","tid":1205518,"uid":93563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:19:58.000Z","msg":"得閒路過見到狗，可唔可以叫佢羅呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:25:15.000Z","msg":"理論上可以，但佢哋會屈你阻差辦公"},{"pid":"94d8ac2b57f4736f107cd35f46787453d9dbec8f","tid":1205518,"uid":44134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}